item.title: CVE-2021-20546|2024-09-16T19:19:34.477Z -- ibm -- spectrum%20protect%20for%20space%20management
item.description: IBM Spectrum Protect Client 8.1.0.0 through 8.1.11.0 is vulnerable to a stack-based buffer overflow, caused by improper bounds checking. A local attacker could overflow a buffer and cause the application to crash. IBM X-Force ID: 198934
